content: That's great to know about Osprey's warranty and customer service! I think I can fit my gym clothes in the main compartment, but I'm not sure about my shoes. I have a pair of bulky gym shoes that might not fit in the side pockets. I'll probably need to carry a separate bag for my gym shoes on Tuesdays and Thursdays. That's okay, though - I'm used to carrying a separate bag for my gym gear anyway. Thanks for the info!
